s. （ <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2023/07/03/opinion/for-most-college-students-affirmative-action-was-not-enough.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">纽约时报</a>）</p><p> • <strong>Black Hole at Heart of Our Galaxy Is on Crash Course, Space-Time Ripples Reveal</strong> : Gravitational waves coming from supermassive black holes like the one at the center of the Milky Way are offering clues to their fates. （ <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/black-hole-gravitational-waves-space-time-d455244d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">华尔街日报</a>）</p><p> • <strong>Dave Grohl&#39;s Monument to Mortality</strong> : With trademark ferocity, the Foo Fighters front man is tackling the capriciousness of sudden loss. （ <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2023/06/foo-fighters-dave-grohl-but-here-we-are/674566/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">大西洋月刊</a>）</p></blockquote><p> Be sure to check out our <a href="https://ritholtz.com/category/podcast/mib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">Masters in Business</a> <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2" data-web-url="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2">interview</a> this weekend with Ilana Weinstein, founder and chief executive officer of <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.theidwgroup.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IDW Group</a> , the top recruiter of fund managers and traders for many of the largest hedge funds.她曾在高盛和波士顿咨询集团工作，并拥有宾夕法尼亚大学和哈佛商学院的学位。</p><p></p><p> <strong>Wildfires caused by fireworks</strong><br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/fireworks.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315829" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/fireworks.png" alt="" width="700" height="502" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/firewo